         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" source="#chaniotisrrrs2016">
            <p>
               <note>A</note>: Made for them while they were still alive
               <note>B</note>: No one else will have the aurhorization to bury anyone, <note> --- etc.</note> will pay a fine of . . .denarii
               <note>C</note>: [This sarcophagus belongs to?] Aurelia Ammias, daughter of [--]oleus, which the aforementioned Ammias bought  [ . .  In this sarcophagus shall also be buried 
               Aurelius?] Polydeukes, and no one else, for he shall pay . . .  denarii to the fiscus.
            </p>
